Clone the Repository
code:
git clone https://github.com/Harshimandava/CropRecommendation.git

Navigate to the Project Directory
code:
cd CropRecommendation


Open index.html in Your Browser
Simply open index.html in your preferred web browser to view the application.

Project Sturcture:
Crop-Recommendation-System/
│
├── images/                 
│   ├── bg4.jpg
│   ├── Cotton.jpg
│   ├── Groundnut.jpg
│   ├── Sunflower.jpg
│   └── ...
│
├── index.html                # Main HTML file
├── crop_recommendation.html  # HTML for crop recommendation page
├── weather.html              # HTML for weather and recommendations page
├── style.css                 # CSS styles for the application
└── script.js                 # JavaScript for dynamic functionalities




